Installation:

* git clone this repo

    git clone https://github.com/lfendy/Vim-Dot-Files.git

* cd to Vim-Dot-Files

* Run install.sh

* Remove (if any) existing .vimrc and .vim directory

* Link .vimrc file and .vim directory to home directory

    (performed inside Vim-Dot-Files dir)
    ln -s ./.vimrc ~/.vimrc && ln -s ./ ~/.vim

* Profit!


Notes:

to fix the maximise button, please use
defaults write org.vim.MacVim MMZoomBoth 1
